            <lg xml:id="TK653">
<l>ōotal vēṇṭu moḷimāḻkuñ ceyviṉai </l>
<l>yāatu meṉṉu mavar</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who say, "we will become (better)" should avoid the performance of acts that would destroy (their fame).</l>
